d 'SAFEDROP': module to drop variables if and only if varnames specified in full
d
d  safedrop drops the variable(s) named if and only if every
d variable name is fully spelled out; that is, even unambiguous
d abbreviations are not indulged. 
d
d KW: drop
d
d Requires: Stata version 8.0
d
d Distribution-Date: 20031022
d
d Author: Nicholas J. Cox, Durham University
d Support: email N.J.Cox@@durham.ac.uk
d
f safedrop.ado
f safedrop.hlp
